      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "The wind will be moderate in some localities. <br/> The weather conditions gave rise to rapid settling of the snowpack. <br/> At higher altitudes, snow cover becomes thinner and patchy; it is better at mid-altitudes, which are less exposed to the wind. Below approximately 2000 m hardly any snow is lying. <br/> The weather conditions gave rise to moistening of the snowpack below approximately 2500 m. <br/> Weak layers exist in the snowpack in particular on steep shady slopes."
      },
